      *              * Progressivi per mese                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-prg-mes-000      thru pmt-prg-mes-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione contatore per progres-          *
      *              * sivi mensili                                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-wrk-cnt-mes          .
       pmt-tes-reg-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Incremento contatore per progressivi        *
      *                  * mensili                                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           add       1                    to   w-wrk-cnt-mes          .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se superiore al massimo si prosegue         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-wrk-cnt-mes        >    12
                     go to pmt-tes-reg-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Nome del mese                                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-nom-mes-000      thru pmt-nom-mes-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Riciclo a mese successivo                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     pmt-tes-reg-100.
       pmt-tes-reg-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Progressivi movimenti di bilancio               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-mov-bil-000      thru pmt-mov-bil-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Data ultima chiusura                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-dat-chi-000      thru pmt-dat-chi-999        .
